PROPRIETARY COMPONENTS NOTE:

The following components of Tantra-LLM are proprietary and subject to special
licensing terms (contact for details):

1. Fusion layer projection weights (~5M params)
2. Adapter parameters (personality/style modules)
3. Memory routing logic (control loop)
4. Identity configuration (behavioral rules)
5. Training prompts for fusion layers

These components define the "soul" of the system and are the primary
proprietary assets. Base models (SpikingBrain, Long-VITA, Whisper) remain
subject to their original licenses.

